cvm_pci_inst_hdr2_t Union Reference

#include <cvm-pci.h>

Detailed Description

Core: The (Packet) Instruction Header appears in the format shown below for Octeon.

Refer to the Octeon HW Manual to read more about the conversion from PCI instruction header to Packet Instruction Header.
